&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Lead, coach, and grow a global, multi-tier support team across regions and time zones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Scale the organization responsibly through hiring, ramp, and career pathing, shifting human roles from repetitive tasks toward high-value, judgment-driven customer interactions.&lt;/li&gt;
